    "ocr": "# 保費回贈優惠 $^{2}$\n\n# Premium Refund Promotion $^{2}$\n\n儲蓄及人壽計劃 Savings and Life Plan \n\n<table><tr><td>指定計劃 Designated Plan</td><td>保費繳付年期 Premium Payment Term</td><td>年度化保費3 Annualized Premium3</td><td colspan=\"2\">保費回贖百分比 Premium Refund Percentage</td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"8\">啟航創富(卓越版) LionAchiever Elite</td><td rowspan=\"4\"><img src=\"images/c40d4442a3659cf7c3ba790920504f421697fbfcb11f4349afdddde0f47f811a.jpg\"/></td><td>&lt; 200,000 (美元/USD)</td><td></td><td><img src=\"images/b2fb3bb0bf7278dd6c4f02be8aaeb18d3829742915b67e3c61a645a31edf04ab.jpg\"/></td></tr><tr><td>≥ 200,000 - &lt; 500,000 (美元/USD)</td><td colspan=\"2\">3%</td></tr><tr><td>≥ 500,000 - &lt; 1,000,000 (美元/USD)</td><td colspan=\"2\">4%</td></tr><tr><td>≥ 1,000,000 (美元/USD)</td><td colspan=\"2\">5%</td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"4\"><img src=\"images/5ed0c180d92529809cdf3fb4d77666b3698222ff64b23f3962c919708f8abfeb.jpg\"/></td><td>&lt; 50,000 (美元/USD)</td><td></td><td>[7G66]</td></tr><tr><td>≥ 50,000 - &lt; 100,000 (美元/USD)</td><td colspan=\"2\">20%</td></tr><tr><td>≥ 100,000 - &lt; 200,000 (美元/USD)</td><td colspan=\"2\">22%</td></tr><tr><td>≥ 200,000 (美元/USD)</td><td colspan=\"2\">25%</td></tr></table>",
