    "ocr": "<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nIllustration of a calculator, clipboard, and coins (no text or symbols)\n</details>\n\n# 保单管理\n\n突发状况发生时，提早安排保单的未来拥有权\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nIcon depicting a person reviewing a document with a clipboard (no text or symbols)\n</details>\n\n# 第二保单持有人\n\n若保单持有人身故或成为精神上无行为能力的人，转移保单拥有权\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nIcon of a document with a shield and cross symbol (no text or numbers)\n</details>\n\n# 保单托管选项\n\n安排临时保单持有人暂时管理保单，直到您的保单继任人准备好接管保单为止",
    "source": "其他/260426_港险优选专家_忠意「启航创富（卓越版）」：短期收益Top1的稳健派神器，定..._185436.md"
