  "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/Uo8SjRYXVdLEy78qREiclsDicn7b9R3icoGav33JLbib3HscXD6qEp9MqlWQScwIrPiarhCCNsg6S1kgAY6G6LuQA1w/640?wx_fmt=other&from=appmsg": {
    "ocr": "<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nSimple line icon depicting a family with a shield and checkmark (no text or symbols)\n</details>\n\n# 世代相传\n\n无缝保单传承\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nSimple line drawing of a person reading a book (no text or symbols)\n</details>\n\n# 保单分拆选项\n\n将保单分拆为多份保单并转移给您的挚爱\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nSimple line drawing of a person presenting in front of a screen (no text or symbols)\n</details>\n\n# 传承权益\n\n\n# 保单延续\n\n当受保人过世，将保单延续并自动转移至受益人\n\n\n# 更换受保人\n\n当受保人仍在世时，\n更改现时受保人",
    "source": "其他/260426_港险优选专家_忠意「启航创富（卓越版）」：短期收益Top1的稳健派神器，定..._185436.md"
  },
  "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/Uo8SjRYXVdLEy78qREiclsDicn7b9R3icoGcHAoAllBjTP6QiaibeJdV3miaich8cCIUPchmdKasQLe1NqDfsd7slf1hQ/640?wx_fmt=other&from=appmsg": {
    "ocr": "# 身故保障支付方式 $^{15}$\n\n本計劃提供多元化的支付方式，透過預先指定的形式以支付總身故保障款項 $^{16}$ 。您可以靈活為每位受益人選擇最合適的支付方式，以滿足他們的個別需要。\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nSimple line drawing of a hand holding a money bag with a dollar sign (no text or symbols)\n</details>\n\n一筆過支付\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nSimple icon of a calendar with a dollar sign, no text or symbols present\n</details>\n\n每月分期支付\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nIllustration of a medical or financial concept with a money bag, plus sign, and calendar (no text or symbols)\n</details>\n\n部份支付：\n\n一筆過支付和每月分期支付的組合，可靈活選擇即時支付或延後支付。",
    "source": "其他/260426_港险优选专家_忠意「启航创富（卓越版）」：短期收益Top1的稳健派神器，定..._185436.md"
  },
  "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/Uo8SjRYXVdLEy78qREiclsDicn7b9R3icoG5QYsWhRt6sY5GDHzrfeibiauqr1aEJ1ztYOkSFCsJHkrjVW7HPtQGkqQ/640?wx_fmt=other&from=appmsg": {
    "ocr": "# 受保人在世時\n\n# While the Insured is alive\n\n保單持有人可即時指定傳承方案\nPolicyholder assigns the legacy,\neffective immediately\n\n\n# 繼續執行該保單\n\n# Continue the Policy\n\n\n更換受保人\n\nChange of Insured\n\n\n保單分拆選項\n\nPolicy Split Option\n\n# 受保人身故時\\*\n\n# Upon Death of the Insured\\*\n\n保單持有人預先訂立傳承方案以應對未來的不測\n\nPolicyholder pre-arranges the legacy for future unfortunate event\n\n\n# 繼續執行該保單\n\n# Continue the Policy\n\n\n保單延續\n\nPolicy Continuation\n\n\n保單分拆選項\n\nPolicy Split Option\n\n\n# 收取總身故保障款項\n\nReceive Total Death\n\nBenefit Payment\n\n\n一筆過支付\n\nLump sum payment\n\n\n每月分期支付\n\nMonthly instalment payment\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>text_image</summary>\n\nIllustration showing a hand holding a money bag and a calendar with a dollar sign, indicating financial or monetary addition.\n</details>\n\n部份支付\n\nPartial payment",
    "source": "其他/260426_港险优选专家_忠意「启航创富（卓越版）」：短期收益Top1的稳健派神器，定..._185436.md"
