    "ocr": "# 忠意集团 — 全球领先的保险公司\n\n香港忠意保险的母公司\n\n# Generali Group – A Leading Global Insurer\n\nParent Company of Generali Hong Kong\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nSimple line drawing of a ribbon or award icon (no text or symbols)\n</details>\n\nA.M. Best 财务实力评级\n\nA+ (截至2024年12月)\n\nA.M. Best\n\nFinancial Strength Rating\n\nA+ (as of Dec 2024)\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nSimple icon of a star inside a circular frame with a ribbon (no text or symbols)\n</details>\n\nFitch财务实力评级\n\nA+ (截至2024年12月)\n\nFitch\n\nFinancial Strength Rating\n\nA+ (as of Dec 2024)\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nSimple line drawing of a five-pointed star on a pedestal (no text or symbols)\n</details>\n\nMoody's 财务实力评级\n\nA3 (截至2024年12月)\n\nMoody's\n\nFinancial Strength Rating\n\nA3 (as of Dec 2024)\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nIllustration of a hand holding a dollar sign with radiating lines (no text or symbols)\n</details>\n\n2024年保费收入达\n\n952亿 欧元\n\n(截至2024年12月)\n\n95.2 billion Euro\n\nin premiums in year 2024\n\n(as of Dec 2024)\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nStylized globe illustration showing continents (no text or labels)\n</details>\n\n全球50多个国家·拥有的\n\n87,000名员工\n\n(截至2024年12月)\n\nAround\n\n87,000 employees\n\nin more than 50 countries\n\n(as of Dec 2024)\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nSimple line drawing of a trophy with two handles and a lid (no text or symbols)\n</details>\n\n在《财富》杂志世界\n\n500强中位震\n\n245位\n\n(截至2024年12月)\n\nRanked\n\n245 $^{th}$\n\nin Fortune Global 500 Companies\n\n(as of Dec 2024)\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>natural_image</summary>\n\nSimple line drawing of a classical building with columns and pediment (no text or symbols)\n</details>\n\n管理资产组模达\n\n8,630亿 欧元\n\n(截至2024年12月)\n\n863 billion Euro\n\nof assets under management\n\n(as of Dec 2024)",
