    "ocr": "# 受保人在世時\n\n# While the Insured is alive\n\n保單持有人可即時指定傳承方案\n\nPolicyholder assigns the legacy, effective immediately\n\n\n# 繼續執行該保單\n\n# Continue the Policy\n\n\n更換受保人\n\nChange of Insured\n\n\n保單分拆選項\n\nPolicy Split Option\n\n# 受保人身故時\\*\n\n# Upon Death of the Insured\\*\n\n保單持有人預先訂立傳承方案以應對未來的不測\n\nPolicyholder pre-arranges the legacy for future unfortunate event\n\n\n# 繼續執行該保單\n\n# Continue the Policy\n\n\n保單延續\n\nPolicy Continuation\n\n\n保單分拆選項\n\nPolicy Split Option\n\n\n# 收取總身故保障款項\n\nReceive Total Death\n\nBenefit Payment\n\n\n一筆過支付\n\nLump sum payment\n\n\n每月分期支付\n\nMonthly instalment payment\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>text_image</summary>\n\nRed icon showing a hand holding a money bag and a calendar with a dollar sign, symbolizing financial or payment growth.\n</details>\n\n部份支付\n\nPartial payment",
