    "ocr": "# Management Discussion and Analysis\n\n# 管理層討論及分析\n\n# INVESTMENT ASSETS\n\nThe table below sets forth the asset allocation of the investment portfolio of the insurance division which the Group uses to monitor the performance of the investment portfolio. The debt securities and loans and receivables were reported at cost less accumulated amortisation and accumulated impairment before expected credit loss while equity securities and unit trusts were reported at fair value.\n\n# 投資資產\n\n下表載列了保險分部投資組合的資產分配，本集團據此監控投資組合的績效。債務證券和貸款及應收款按成本減累計攤銷和累計減值及預期信用損失前列報，而權益證券和單位信託則按公允價值列報。\n\n<table><tr><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"></td><td colspan=\"2\">As at 31 December於十二月三十一日</td></tr><tr><td>2024二零二四年HK$ million百萬港元</td><td>2023二零二三年HK$ million百萬港元</td></tr><tr><td>General investment and surplus assets</td><td>一般投資及剩餘資產</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Debt securities</td><td>債務證券</td><td>62,834</td><td>61,172</td></tr><tr><td>Loans and receivables</td><td>貸款及應收款</td><td>4,317</td><td>5,035</td></tr><tr><td>Equity securities</td><td>權益證券</td><td>2,590</td><td>2,436</td></tr><tr><td>Cash for investment</td><td>用於投資的現金</td><td>1,948</td><td>475</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"></td><td>71,689</td><td>69,118</td></tr><tr><td>Direct participating contracts</td><td>具有直接參與分紅特點的合同</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Debt securities</td><td>債務證券</td><td>4,413</td><td>1,317</td></tr><tr><td>Equity securities</td><td>權益證券</td><td>3,366</td><td>2,060</td></tr><tr><td>Cash for investment</td><td>用於投資的現金</td><td>859</td><td>1,840</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"></td><td>8,638</td><td>5,217</td></tr><tr><td>Unit-linked</td><td>投資相連</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Equity securities</td><td>權益證券</td><td>5,663</td><td>5,748</td></tr></table>",
