ched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"2\">Z-Retire Pro退休保Z-Retire Pro Insurance</td><td>週年紅利Annual Dividend</td><td>全部All</td><td>不適用N/A</td><td>不適用N/A</td><td>不適用N/A</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td></tr><tr><td>終期紅利Terminal Dividend</td><td>全部All</td><td>不適用N/A</td><td>不適用N/A</td><td>不適用N/A</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td><td>尚未推出Not yet launched</td></tr></table>\n\n註：  \nNotes:   \n豐盛逸悅保 / Z-Retire Pro 退休保：  \nLionPromise Pro / Z-Retire Pro Insurance:   \n週年紅利 / 終期紅利的實現率於某些保單年度顯示為「不適用」，因為：  \nThe fulfillment ratio for Annual Dividend / Terminal Dividend is shown as \"N/A\" for some policy years because:\n\n\\- 週年紅利/終期紅利於相應的保單年度內並未開始提供，故分紅實現率不能釐定；或\n\nAnnual Dividend / Terminal Dividend is not yet available in the corresponding policy years, so the fulfillment ratio is undetermined; or\n\n\\- 就終期紅利而言，於該報告年度中並沒有相關保單終止或沒有相關保單獲支付終期紅利，故沒有可披露的數字。\n\nfor Terminal Dividend, no relevant policies terminated or no relevant policies received Terminal Dividend in the reporting year and therefore there is no reportable statistics.",
