    "ocr": "![](images/b49f9500df33de8235406b35b5a200e2c86658d65d82db4d96478b6f08d9c1bb.jpg)\n\n<details>\n<summary>flowchart</summary>\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    A[\"The Premium you pay\\n(One-time or scheduled payment)\"] -- > B[\"Net Premium\"]\n    C[\"Deduct Premium Charges\"] -.-> B\n    B -- > D[\"Fixed Account\"]\n    D -- > E[\"Enjoy a guaranteed lock-in crediting rate²\\nin the first policy year.\"]\n    D -- > F[\"Get a minimum guaranteed crediting rate\\nof 2% p.a. thereafter.\"]\n    B -- > G[\"Guaranteed Loyalty Bonus Crediting Rate\\nof 0.35% p.a. from the 11P Policy Year\\nonwards up to age 100 of the Life Assured.\"]\n    B -- > H[\"Index Account\"]\n    H -- > I[\"Benefit from potentially higher returns³.\"]\n    H -- > J[\"Crediting rate is based on the performance\\nof S&P 500 Index and Nasdaq-100 Index,\\nsubject to floor and cap rates by Singlife.\"]\n    D -- > K[\"Deduct Monthly Charges\"]\n    K -.-> L[\"Account Value of the Policy\"]\n```\n</details>",
