  "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/vv6EicHFdTb1F2pCxlMFpnh9vWRpzONxDPmcIcPeuJOpaqcI369sUccXF6znjOezAiaDQXnwDDaWibOLlRNp01B7eJOolXsSiafYvdqT6WJACrc/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg": {
    "ocr": "# ABOUT CHINA TAIPING\n\n# 關於中國太平\n\n中國太平保險集團有限責任公司，簡稱「中國太平」，於1929年在上海創立，是我國歷史上持續經營最為悠久的民族保險品牌，也是我國唯一一家管理總部在境外的中醫金融企業。\n\n2023年，中國太平實踰營業收入1,346萬元，年末總資產1.37萬元，管理投資資產2.3萬元，已成餘擁有24家主要成員公司及2,000股與各個營業機構的大型跨匯金融保険集團。\n\n中國太平跨境經營、業務範圍巡查機關、財務、農老保險、再保險、再保險經紀及保險代理、互聯網保險、資產管理、證券經紀、金融租賃、不動產投資、舊老醫療健康產業等領域。\n\n中國太平鐘部設在香港，在中國境內、中國香港、中國澳門、英國、新加坡、印尼、盧森堡、日本、澳大利亞、南非、泰國、迪拜等設立機構，並與全球130整個國家建立業務往來，是中國保險業在境外擁有最多分支機構的金融保險集團。\n\n\\*应解释罚款：费常单位加人民用。\n\nChina Taiping Insurance Group Co., Ltd. (referred to as \"China Taiping\") was founded in Shanghai in 1929. It is the longest-running national insurance brand in China's history, as well as the only central financial enterprise headquartered in Hong Kong.\n\nIn 2023, China Taiping's operation revenue exceeds 134.6 billion yuan, total assets exceeds 1.37 trillion yuan, and assets under management reaches over 2.3 trillion yuan. It is a large multinational financial and insurance group with more than 500 thousand employees, 24 subsidiaries and more than 2,000 entities at all levels.\n\nChina Taiping's multinational business covers life insurance, general insurance, pension insurance, reinsurance, reinsurance brokerage, and insurance agency, online insurance, asset management, securities brokerage, financial leasing, real estate investment, and elderly care, medical and health industries.\n\nHeadquarter based in Hong Kong, China Taiping has established subsidiaries in Chinese mainland, Chinese Hong Kong, Chinese Macau, the United Kingdom, Singapore, Indonesia, Luxembourg, Japan, Australia, South Africa, Thailand, Dubai, etc. and extended its business to 130 countries around the world, making it the financial insurance group with the most overseas branches in China's insurance industry.\n\n\"Unless stated otherwise, the currency is in CHV.\"",
    "source": "微信搜索结果/260519_国寿、中银、太平、太保，中资香港4大保司，哪家产品最值得买？.md"
  },
