  "https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/vv6EicHFdTb3rOTS2nMNDmLBzHWtCJuMticborZqGu6kOcZO5uUdOutiaTyDQY7K8uPaEbETib1thnTXxkdxkwibvJjvUUD60OcJgib1xLv158UHI/640?wx_fmt=png&from=appmsg": {
    "ocr": "# 中國太平養老社區\n\n中國太平養老社區以CCRC持續照料退休社區為主，為長者提供自理、介護、介助一體化的居住設施和服務。所有社區擁有豐富醫療資源，構建以醫療護理、康復為核心，健康管理服務一體化的綜合服務體系，致力於滿足客戶多樣化、差異化、品質化的綜合服務需求，為客戶提供一站式的養老服務解決方案。如今，中國太平養老社區已遍佈全國，數量突破67家。自建自營養老社區床位突破1萬張。這不僅代表中國太平在養老服務領域的堅定步伐，更彰顯了我們為長者打造高品質養老生活的承諾。\n\n# China Taiping CCRC Community\n\nChina Taiping Elderly Care Communities primarily focus on CCRC (Continuing Care Retirement Community) models, offering integrated living facilities and services for the elderly that include self-care, assisted care, and assisted living. All communities are equipped with abundant medical resources, establishing a comprehensive service system that integrates medical care, rehabilitation, and health management services. The aim is to meet the diverse, differentiated, and high-quality comprehensive service needs of clients, providing a one-stop solution for elderly care services. Today, China Taiping Elderly Care Communities are spread nationwide, with the number exceeding 67. The number of beds in self-built elderly care community facilities has surpassed 10,000. This not only represents China Taiping's firm steps in the field of elderly care services, but also demonstrates our commitment to creating a high-quality life for the elderly.",
    "source": "微信搜索结果/260519_国寿、中银、太平、太保，中资香港4大保司，哪家产品最值得买？.md"
